{"Id":826970,"Title":"浣溪纱 夜坐","Dynasty":"清","Author":"樊增祥","Context":"画鼓无声静晚衙。小池芳树带栖鸦。香销酒醒在天涯。密密书缄江上锦，昏昏灯结雨中花。自笼纱帽自煎茶。春后恹恹损带围。楚人词里送将归。愁听梁燕语依依。有酒惟浇金范蠡，无花可拟画杨妃。垆香如水织帘垂。烛意凉来觉渐亲。潇湘枕簟暗生尘。里头闲坐讽汀蘋。夜雨低徊心上事，朝云依约画中人。隔墙钗钏久无闻。独夜生憎更漏长。聊凭墨牒遣流光。迎梅天气越凄凉。蜜酒定无通夜力，罗衣还发隔年香。无多闲事尽思量。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":2,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"f8af88a05043104649686ea5635b2fbe","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":5773072,"Sentence":"画鼓无声静晚衙。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"huà gǔ mó shēng jìng wǎn yá ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5773074,"Sentence":"香销酒醒在天涯。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xiāng xiāo jiu xing zài tiān yá ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5773075,"Sentence":"密密书缄江上锦，昏昏灯结雨中花。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"mì mì shū jiān jiāng shǎng jin ，hūn hūn dēng jiē yǔ zhōng huā ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5773076,"Sentence":"自笼纱帽自煎茶。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zì lóng shā mào zì jiān chá ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5773077,"Sentence":"春后恹恹损带围。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"chūn hòu yān yān sǔn dài wéi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5773078,"Sentence":"楚人词里送将归。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"chǔ rén cǐ li sòng jiāng guī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5773079,"Sentence":"愁听梁燕语依依。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"chóu tīng liáng yān yǔ yī yī ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5773080,"Sentence":"有酒惟浇金范蠡，无花可拟画杨妃。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yǒu jiu wéi jiāo jīn fàn lǐ ，mó huā kě ni huà yáng fēi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":8,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5773082,"Sentence":"烛意凉来觉渐亲。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zhú yì liáng lái jiào jiān qīn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"Engl